#&quot;Just Look at Me Now&quot; (T. Bachman, Turner) – 4:38
#&quot;My Sugaree&quot; (R. Bachman) – 3:47
#&quot;City&#x27;s Still Growin&#x27;&quot; (Turner) – 5:44
#&quot;Another Fool&quot; (R. Bachman) – 5:29
#&quot;Lost in a Fantasy&quot; (R. Bachman) – 4:11
#&quot;Toledo&quot; (Turner) – 4:12
#&quot;Service with a Smile&quot; (R. Bachman) – 4:21

