<doc id="1119918" wikidata="Q2089691" url="?curid=1119918" title="Boa Esperança, Espírito Santo">
<text>Boa Esperança is a municipality located in the Brazilian state of Espírito Santo. Its population was 15,092 (2020) and its area is 429 km². Its average altitude is 140 meters above sea level.

