<doc id="1119976" wikidata="Q668992" url="?curid=1119976" title="Jaguaré">
<text>Jaguaré is a municipality located in the Brazilian state of Espírito Santo. Its population was 31,039 (2020) and its area is 660 km2.

The municipality contains part of the Sooretama Biological Reserve, a strictly protected conservation unit created in 1982 when two earlier units were merged.

